the gay divorcee is a 1934 american musical film directed by mark sandrich and starring fred astaire and ginger rogers.http://www.reelclassics.com/teams/fred&ginger/fred&ginger2.htm   it also features alice brady , edward everett horton , eric blore and erik rhodes , and was based on the broadway musical gay divorce written by dwight taylor from an unproduced play by j. hartley manners , which was adapted into a musical by kenneth s. webb and samuel hoffenstein."screenplay ino " on tcm.com

